%e A113830 Here is the beginning of Granville's table:
%e A113830   n GAP          Last term
%e A113830   2 3+8*i+2*j        13
%e A113830   3 7+24*i+6*j       43
%e A113830   4 5+36*i+6*j       59
%e A113830   5 11+96*i+30*j    227
%e A113830   6 11+42*i+60*j    353
%e A113830   7 47+132*i+210*j 1439
